01:26:11.234 --> 01:26:13.602
My whole life was there.

01:26:15.304 --> 01:26:16.472
Where will you go?

01:26:18.541 --> 01:26:20.543
With you.

01:26:20.576 --> 01:26:23.546
I don't know
where I'm going,

01:26:23.579 --> 01:26:26.449
